Package: deconverse
Type: Package
Title: Bulk deconvolution methods from single-cell references
Version: 0.2.6.7
Author: Clarice S Groeneveld
Maintainer: Clarice S Groeneveld <clari.groeneveld@gmail.com>
Description: This package implements wrappers for methods of bulk RNA-seq 
    deconvolution using single-cell data to build cell population profiles.
    Using pseudobulk simulations, deconverse also allows for benchmarking and 
    comparing different deconvolution methods in a context-specific manner.
Depends: R (> 4.0), tidyverse
Remotes:
    csgroen/ggheatmapper,
    jamesotto852/ggdensity
